    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the style, culture, and period of the historic West Turkestani region before the Turkmen Soviet Socialist republic was formed in 1924. For the style and culture pertaining to the area of Turkmenistan after 1924, use "Turkmen."</Note_Text>
